{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "29", "m": "05", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "23", "M": "01", "S": "22"}}, "news": [{"title": "Shriram Properties targets \u20b93,750-4,000 crore pre-sales in FY27, expects Pune to overtake Chennai", "para": "Shriram Properties expects to clock \u20b93,750-4,000 crore of pre-sales in FY27 and remains on track to meet its FY28 targets, said Murali Malayappan, chairman & managing director, and Gopalakrishnan J, executive director & CEO, Shriram Properties. The company plans to deepen its presence in Bengaluru, Chennai, Pune and Kolkata, while evaluating Mumbai and selectively looking at office, data centre and rental housing opportunities.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/shriram-properties-aims-for-4000-crore-pre-sales-by-fy27-pune-to-surpass-chennai/131387232?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-79874/131387232.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "PPCB flags compliance gaps, urges builders to follow EC norms in Zirakpur", "para": "The Punjab Pollution Control Board (PPCB) met with the Builders Welfare Association in Zirakpur to emphasize environmental compliance and adherence to Environmental Clearance (EC) conditions. Officials urged builders to display guidelines on-site, accurately self-file applications, and prepare for monsoon by cleaning rainwater harvesting systems and ensuring efficient STPs for sustainable urban growth.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/ppcb-urges-compliance-from-builders-in-zirakpur-for-environmental-protection/131388698?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-81310/131388698.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Godrej Family Office, JSW Family Office, Lodha and Sattva Family Office invest in SILA", "para": "S